            <p><strong>Structure:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Issue introduction with current data (2 minutes)</li>
                <li>Multiple perspectives analysis (4 minutes)</li>
                <li>Evidence evaluation and fact-checking (2 minutes)</li>
                <li>Reasoned recommendations (2 minutes)</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Requirements:</strong> Cite 4+ credible sources, address counter-arguments, show cultural awareness</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="assessment-option">
